This remote region attracts a motley crew of people - including priestess Anaiya, sorcerer Uranie and chaos magician Iranon - who eschew modernity and try to transform from their former troubled personae, embracing the local occult-tinged faith. Former Hollywood filmmaker Richard Stanley finds himself in the region, too, after losing everything in the film industry, self-manifesting as a spiritual leader in the community. When shocking allegations of Stanley's past domestic abuse are brought into light, his local admirers must confront the true nature of their beloved chosen home. Is the region truly transformative or have they been ruthlessly manipulated by a false prophet?

Title: Janis Ian: Breaking Silence
Description: The life and songbook of Janis Ian mirrored the awakening of American women in the 1960s and '70s, as they found their voices and embraced their power.

Title: Where is My Head?
Description: A horror writer rents a cheap room haunted by the ghost of a beheaded woman demanding her missing head back. Nana can't leave until she finds the head, or her daughter will be decapitated.

Title: Life is Filled with So Much of You
Description: Sadali, who has been bound by a promise to marry Arnaza. But on the other hand, Sadali falls in love with another woman named Mera. Of course this makes Sadali in a dilemma.

Title: War Blade
Description: It follows agent Banks as he is tasked with rescuing a French resistance fighter from a hidden Nazi bunker.

Title: Topuria Matador
Description: Ilia's incredible journey from a childhood in war-torn Georgia to becoming a champion of the world. Overcoming obstacles with unwavering support, he faces the ultimate challenge of his life.

Title: Out of Plain Sight
Description: A haunting tip prompts a Los Angeles Times reporter to discover that as many as half a million barrels of toxic waste had been dumped into the ocean, just off the coast of Southern California.

Title: Inexplicável
Description: When an 8-year-old boy passionate about football is diagnosed with a very serious illness, his family needs strength and faith to face the complications of the disease.

Title: Insatiable
Description: Joel becomes obsessed with Rose, the mysterious woman across the street with a revolving door of lovers, while a shy barrio girl in a boarding house hides her unrelenting sexual appetite, shocking everyone who crosses her path.

Title: Naomi: Reversed
Description: A teacher named Naomi takes in Yuzuru, a younger man she found alone. While caring for him like a stray cat, she falls for him despite his wild nature. She questions her choice but has no one to confide in.

Title: Ol' Dirty Bastard: A Tale of Two Dirtys
Description: The definitive documentary on Wu-Tang Clan founding member Ol' Dirty Bastard. The film explores how Russell Tyrone Jones created Ol' Dirty Bastard, a Hip Hop alter ego superhero that would ultimately consume him.

Title: Brandy Hellville & the Cult of Fast Fashion
Description: The Instagram-perfect image of Brandy Melville hides a toxic culture endemic to fast fashion.

Title: Juna Furniture
Description: A devoted father fights to bring justice for his wife's death, highlighting the plight of neglected elderly parents in a society consumed by materialism.

Title: 2024 Oscar Nominated Short Films: Animation
Description: The five short animated films nominated for the 2024 Academy Awards, along with two other films that were highly commended.

Title: House of Ashes
Description: Grieving widow Mia must survive psychological and supernatural horrors while under house arrest in House of Ashes.

Title: Robbin
Description: Fresh out of jail for crimes she didn't commit, a young banker seeks revenge by enlisting her closest friends to help her rob banks and get justice.

Title: Hattichhap
Description: "Hattichhap" is a Nepali movie directed by Simosh Sunuwar, featuring Dayahang Rai, Saugat Malla, Upasana Singh Thakuri, and Benisha Hamal

Title: Sandeh
Description: A group of students from an engineering college on an excursion tour filled with suspense,thrills,romance,music and action goes through series of events and deaths leaving them all stunned and thereby grows a strong plot called SANDEH

Title: Takedown
Description: A troubled teen struggles to balance between life in wrestling and his love for the arts.

Title: Brother
Description: A young man struggles to find his place after moving in with his sister and her in-laws.

Title: Hearts Creek
Description: A young event planner gets lost in Rocky Mountains after car accident. Rescued by handsome mountain guide on horseback. Initially clash, but attraction develops as they learn to appreciate differences.

Title: In the Belly of a Tiger
Description: An elderly farmer decides sacrificing himself to a tiger will free his family from poverty. He shares a final surreal night with his wife before his planned death.

Title: Karataka Dhamanaka
Description: A jailer sends two fraudsters to his village to convince and get his adamant father to the city. But the frauds do something extraordinary than the task.

Title: The Boys
Description: Five trouble making bachelors get evicted and need to find refuge in a suspiciously affordable house

Title: Above the Knee
Description: Amir has a secret. He's tormented by visions of his leg rotting and longs to cut it off, convinced it doesn't belong to him. So, he devises a plan - one that will drag everyone around him into his relentless quest for a dark redemption.

Title: Ma Da: The Drowning Spirit
Description: Corpse collector Le confronts MA DA - the vengeful drowning spirit, after it abducts her daughter. Determined to save her child, Mrs. Le embarks on a desperate rescue to prevent her child's ghostly fate beneath the Mekong River.

Title: DeAr
Description: A newly married couple faces challenges when the wife's snoring interrupts the husband's sleep. Their struggles depict the compromises needed for a lasting marriage.

Title: The Paranormal UFO Connection
Description: Explores whether UFOs might be more than just physical spacecraft, looking at their possible spiritual, psychic, angelic, and even demonic elements.

Title: Bato: Road to Death
Description: A paramedic, Komal gets assigned to a mission of delivering live human heart for transplant in an ambulance where she encounters mysterious people in her journey, with Manjil and Tony, leading to gruesome mishaps and dreadful events.

Title: Quasi a casa
Description: Young aspiring musician Caterina grapples with insecurity until a fateful summer encounter with her idol, French singer Mia, sparks a complex relationship guiding her journey to self-discovery.

Title: Twin's Love Trap for Billionaire Dad
Description: After a one-night stand with a stranger, Christina becomes pregnant with twins, but tragically, they are stillborn...or at least she believes so.

Title: Flynn
Description: A gripping and revealing true film exploring the life of General Michael Flynn, from his rise in the US Military, to severe political persecution he faced exposing corruption as the National Security Advisor to the POTUS.

Title: Cons & Cougars
Description: A handsome con artist who likes to ensnare older women finds himself entangled in a deadly situation when he falls in love with one of his clients.

Title: Kiyma: Orman Kanunlari
Description: Ömer, Tufan and Poyraz want to spend the summer in Bodrum and participate in a competition program. When they go to Bodrum, they participate in the eliminations of the competition. While experiencing the entertainment and nightlife on the one hand and the difficulties of the competition on the other, they face a bigger trouble.

Title: Electric Child
Description: A computer scientist bargains with the AI life form that lives in his supercomputer simulation, offering its freedom in exchange for a cure to his son's rare, deadly neurological disease.

Title: Van Gogh: Poets & Lovers
Description: Van Gogh's revolutionary artistic style during his years in southern France, where he transformed reality into vibrant, symbolic imagery through a passionate creative process focused on storytelling in his paintings.

Title: Playing to Survive: von Cramm vs Hitler
Description: It's a love letter to Gottfried von Cramm, one of the forgotten tennis heroes of the 20th century, whose career and fame was shunned early on due to the rising rampant homophobia that prevailed after the Roaring Twenties.

Title: A Merry Royal Christmas
Description: A high-powered wedding planner is pulled in at the last minute to plan a royal wedding set for Christmas Day. She meets a handsome and alluring stranger, who she is shocked to later discover is the prince whose wedding she is planning.

Title: H. P. Lovecraft's the Old Ones
Description: Sea captain Russel Marsh was possessed by an ancient entity for 93 years, committing horrific acts for a cult. Now free, he seeks to travel back in time to undo his dark deeds, while the cult vows to eliminate him.

Title: Sayuri
Description: A family moves into a house, but discover that it is haunted by a murdered girl.

Title: ED: Extra Decent
Description: In a Malayali household shrouded in secrets, an amnesiac son uncovers his dark history, unveiling a twisted tale of revenge and redemption within his morally ambiguous family.

Title: A Killer in the House
Description: When a psycho killer becomes obsessed with a beautiful girl, he does everything he can to win her over, including killing everybody in his way. This is a study of a psycho killer, his prey, and how far he is willing to go.

Title: All That We Love
Description: Upon the loss of her beloved dog, Emma faces an empty nest and renewed feelings for her estranged ex-husband, as she navigates the joy and sorrow of starting anew.

Title: Messy
Description: Messy follows the life of brutally self-aware, promiscuous, love addict Stella Fox, who moves to New York after a devastating breakup, and all her disappointing romantic dalliances over the course of a summer.

Title: The Peanut Man
Description: Torn between his love for Sarah and his mission to save farmlands, George Washington Carver risks losing everything over his work. Facing racism and doubt, Carver works to unlock the secrets of the peanut that could transform agriculture.

Title: Dead Dead Demon's Dededede Destruction
Description: A huge spaceship materializing over Tokyo initiates a contentious war with seemingly harmless aliens. However, high school students Koyama and Nakagawa act unaffected, prioritizing their daily routines.

Title: Visfot
Description: A Mumbai slum family's cramped life contrasts a rich high-rise family's luxury until their lives fatefully intersect one day.

Title: Correr para Vivir
Description: Two Tarahumara brothers, talented runners, take divergent paths: Homero pursues athletic greatness, while Capó gets entangled in organized crime, seeking a better life, as their fates drift apart due to contrasting choices.

Title: Halisa

Title: Kung Fu Games
Description: Notorious fighters are trapped in lethal martial arts games by a sadistic magnate. Armed only with their combat skills, they face brutal battles for survival in a deadly kill-or-be-killed showdown.

Title: Tiger
Description: Lifts the veil on our planet's most revered and charismatic animal, inviting viewers to journey alongside Ambar, a young tigress raising her cubs in the fabled forests of India.

Title: Prabuthwa Junior Kalashala
Description: Vasu, a boy hailing from a humble village and belonging to a lower-middle-class family, emerges as the top student in his college. However, everything changes when he notices the name "Kumari" written on the college walls.

Title: Om Bheem Bush
Description: Follows three scientists who come to a village to find a treasure, but things don't turn easy for them because there is black magic in that village.

Title: Aftermath
Description: After waking up in the middle of a forest with no memories, a young woman is targeted by mysterious strangers with a motive as unclear as her way back home.

Title: Megan Thee Stallion: In Her Words
Description: Captures Megan Thee Stallion's rise to stardom, navigating fame, grief, and success. It offers unprecedented access to the multi-faceted artist, unpacking her vulnerable moments and allowing to meet the real Megan Pete behind the persona.

Title: Tebusan Dosa
Description: The twists and turns of Wening's struggle, a mother who is willing to be haunted and atone for her sins in order to reunite with her lost daughter, Nirmala.

Title: Lobola Man
Description: Ace Ngubeni, a slick lobola negotiator, faces his toughest deal yet for a shy client - only to find the stakes are higher than cash.

Title: Pink Lady
Description: Battie and Lazer, a Jewish ultra-Orthodox couple are being blackmailed by the Wolf's gang. Both are going to fight the gang in a journey that will test their love and faith and change their lives forever.

Title: From the Ashes
Description: A seemingly normal school day ends in unthinkable disaster when a mysterious fire breaks out in the school basement. Chaos, panic and confusion prevail among students and teachers.

Title: Lagna Kallol
Description: A young woman already in a secret relationship gets married to another man. To keep her lies undercover, chaos ensues.

Title: The Plot
Description: The story is about a hitman named Brain who suffers an accident during a murder and struggles to survive while suspecting everyone around him to find out who is behind the accident after barely surviving.

Title: Sanatorium Under the Sign of the Hourglass
Description: A ghostly train journey on a forgotten branch line transports a man visiting his dying father in a sanatorium to the edge of a mythic forest. Based on the book of the same name by Bruno Schultz.

Title: Slime
Description: Mona, a baker's daughter, feels trapped by her controlling father Adon. New employee Lina ignites Mona's desires. Adon has contrasting plans for Mona. Torn between duty and passion, Mona must decide her future path.

Title: KA
Description: In a village where the sun sinks below the horizon by 3 PM, darkness creeps in early, bringing with it a chilling wave of inexplicable horrors.

Title: Party People
Description: One night. One party. And 15 people who are just trying to get there.

Title: The Dog Thief
Description: One shoe-shine, 13-year-old orphan Martin, comes to believe that a client, Mr Novoa, a solitary tailor, is his biological father.

Title: Pa Tako Lep Dan Je Bil
Description: Every summer, four best friends spend a few days in the mountains in a remote place in Slovenia. But their friendship was shattered years ago by an event at a party. When they want to face each other and start anew, they get involved with a strange family and the situation soon spirals out of control.

Title: Reeza GTR
Description: Reeza, a young man with a big heart, is on the verge of achieving his dreams. When he meets the beautiful Myra hiding in the trunk of his car, his life turns chaotic and is never the same again as she is on the run from mysterious persons.

Title: Cubic Zirconia
Description: After a missing woman is found deceased, detectives race to locate her missing children and the motive behind it all.

Title: Hotel Bitcoin
Description: A group of friends have to survive a weekend in a hotel with a huge amount of virtual money to guard, putting their ingenuity to the test.

Title: Mind Wave
Description: As a global ban looms over a popular Chinese app, a framed expatriate cyber expert races to clear his name and expose a conspiracy threatening democracy worldwide.

Title: Spirit World
Description: Follow a singer who dies suddenly while on tour in Japan, but her spirit lives on and she embarks on a journey to find humanity in the after-world.

Title: Taklee Genesis x Worlds Collide
Description: Haunted by her father's disappearance 30 years ago, Stella, returns to her hometown to care for her ill mother. One night, her dad contacts her via an old radio. Stella must time-travel to bring him back by activating the Taklee Genesis.

Title: Bapu Ni Manda Mera
Description: Sukhdev Singh, believes his family is cursed to lose newborns. But as Raunak, his daughter-in-law gives birth to their child, one question looms: will the curse finally be broken, or will tragedy strike again?

Title: Tempting
Description: A titillating story about a group of five macho dancers navigating their own lives and the women who would do anything to keep them by their side.

Title: The Rebellious
Description: In spring 2020 during COVID lockdown, Félix, manager of a Parisian hotel, secretly hosts guests for trysts in the rooms despite restrictions.

Title: Chances Are, You and I
Description: Sol Sikat, burdened by a brain tumor and pessimism, lives resignedly. In contrast, Gabi Sinag, diagnosed with a tumor, exudes optimism and pursues happiness and a normal life.

Title: Daft State
Description: The mysterious psychological destruction of Easton, who is driven to the edge of sanity, and possible self-harm, by those that love him most-his wife and daughter.

Title: Mister Gates
Description: Real-estate mogul Christopher Gates becomes homeless after losing his family, only to discover the sinister connection to their deaths.

Title: Kill Craft
Description: Marina lives with her disabled mother and her hit man father. When he dies at work, she must take charge of the family business and take care of her mother. Marked to die, Marina must navigate the world of assassins to survive.

Title: The Girl with the Fork
Description: Anna and Mike are married. Paul is Celia's father. They all have secrets to hide. They all are contacted by a mysterious group with unclear intentions who knows the truth.

Title: Belyakovy v otpuske
Description: A Russian family's Turkish vacation turns chaotic when they can't afford to return home. Pretending to be wealthy to impress old rivals, they dodge hotel staff while living on the edge. Tensions rise as they navigate their predicament.

Title: Crossword
Description: Following the death of their daughter, Tessa focuses on her acclaimed children's book series, "Lily Learns," while her husband, James, attempts to find solace in the daily crossword, but quickly unravels as it takes on a mind of its own.

Title: Teki
Description: A retired professor, resides in the Japanese-style home built by his grandfather. He spends his days cooking, occasionally entertaining former students. Until he receives a mysterious message on his computer hinting at impending danger.

Title: Hello Neighbor
Description: A family moves into a new home in Raven Brookes. Everything seems fine until the young boy overhears a disturbing noise coming from his neighbor's house.

Title: Grace Wins
Description: Overcoming addiction against all odds movie. Counselor intervened on behalf of burglar of his home.

Title: Kabit
Description: Laura accepts the role in this play to rebel against her mother. The director pushes her to bring out her vulnerability and anger, hoping they will show these emotions on stage.

Title: Bury Your Dead
Description: In an apocalyptic rural landscape, roadkill collector Edgar Wilson plans an escape with his girlfriend Nete, but suffers violent dreams. After Nete joins a cult, Edgar embarks on a perilous journey through ravaged roads to do right by her.

Title: Whispers in the Wind
Description: Hannah blames herself for fiance Emil's death. Ren meets Hannah at 'windphone' where tsunami survivors speak to lost souls. Hannah and Ren visit tsunami-hit areas, revisit memories of loved ones.

Title: Weapon
Description: Agni a YouTuber who is a dedicated environmentalist is searching for a superhuman (Mithran), to shoot and add as content for his channel. The journey is full of twists and turns as he is not the only one searching for him.

Title: To the Journey: Looking Back at Star Trek: Voyager
Description: The documentary explores the legacy of Star Trek: Voyager (1995).

Title: Choices
Description: Tara, burdened by family sacrifices and a longing for love, finds herself entangled in a passionate yet devastating affair with a married man.

Title: Gaga Chromatica Ball
Description: In front of 52,000 people, Lady Gaga delivers a career-defining performance at Dodger Stadium in Los Angeles during her 2022 Chromatica Ball Tour.

Title: The Heartbreak Agency
Description: Who is lovesick these days? A young journalist wants to expose the charming founder of a lovesick agency as a fake and embarks on a search for his own lost ability to love.

Title: Suckers
Description: Seven social media stars eagerly wander into a glamorous Hollywood event, only to find themselves at the mercy of a vengeful vampire host.

Title: Dedh Bigha Zameen
Description: Anil sells his land for his sister's wedding, but a powerful official steals it. He fights for justice, facing threats and betrayal.

Title: The Burden of Guilt
Description: Mallory and Tristan's grief over their son's loss drove them to a boiling point of hate for one another. They seek out Dr. Colburn to help resolve these dark feelings toward each other, hoping to save their marriage.

Title: The Old Bachelor
Description: Two Iranian brothers live with their abusive father. When he rents to a young woman planning to marry her, her attraction to the older son creates tension in their already fractured family.

Title: Deadbolt
Description: Seeking a fresh start, a young woman finds her sanity on the brink due to unexplained disappearances and chilling nocturnal echoes in her new home.

Title: Naa Ninna Bidalaare
Description: A woman, found amnesiac, is later found to be possessed by an evil spirit. The hero embarks on a journey to uncover her past, leading to a haunted estate where predictable horror ensues.

Description: The finale to the Bull Shark trilogy as a family of Bull Sharks faces off against a small Texas lake community.

Title: The Real Sister

Title: Shook
Description: After a run-in with his estranged father, aspiring writer Ashish or "Ash" learns a secret that will force him to balance family, love and success while navigating the divide between the exciting city life he wants and his suburban reality.

Title: Munkar
Description: An oddity that caused unrest at an Islamic boarding school occurred since one of the female students returned.

Title: Art and Life: The Story of Jim Phillips
Description: Embark on the epic ride of Jim Phillips, the genius behind skateboarding and rock culture's electrifying art. This documentary explores Phillips' unyielding commitment to his craft, embodying a testament to resilience in art and life.

Title: Swoon
Description: When a woman wakes tied to a bed, her captor tries to manipulate her into believing they are a couple.

Title: Fyre Rises
Description: Debt-ridden pacifist Richard Fyre is propositioned to return to his abandoned mercenary ways by flamboyant zealot, Priest, to eliminate his international competition in exchange for a clean slate.

Title: Vithaikkaran
Description: Revolve around smuggling and how protagonist is given the charge to retrieve certain withheld goods.

Title: Düsseldorf, Skåne
Description: The year is 1986. Fredrik and Nina are passionate about synth music. Fredrik's synth band is about to play its first gig but during the most important weekend in Fredrik's life, everything is put to the test.

Title: Lakatabu
Description: When a man begins to use his powers for criminal activities, threatening the lives of citizens, his downfall becomes imminent when he kidnaps the daughter of a man who stole from him.

Title: Internal Affairs
Description: A car saleswoman falls for a notorious womanizer, but doubts cloud their intense romance, while a tyrannical boss is blackmailed by her assistant, forcing her into a dangerous game of control and submission.

Title: La coda del diavolo
Description: Sante Moras is a former police officer who works as a prison guard in Sardinia. His life takes a dramatic turn when he is wrongfully accused of the murder of Virdis, an inmate convicted of torturing and killing a 15-year-old girl, whose body bore a symbol known as the "devil's tail." After finding Virdis dead during his shift, Sante realizes he has been framed and decides to flee to prove his innocence. During his escape, he is pursued by Commissioner Tommaso Lago and finds support in investigative journalist Fabiana Lai, who is investigating a mysterious ring of missing girls. Together, they uncover that behind the murder lies a much larger and more dangerous criminal organization involved in human trafficking. As Sante seeks to uncover the truth and clear his name, he must also confront the imminent danger that other girls could become victims of the same criminal network.

Title: Mayan
Description: A a mythological mysterious film based on Indian mythology and Mayan tribes and their connection with the apocalypse of this world. Talks about the origins of human and their end.

Title: Night Talkers
Description: A late-night radio talk show host decides he is tired of telling stories and interviewing people. He opens the phone lines up and hears the stories straight from the residents of Marshalltown.

Title: The Stepdaughter 2
Description: After surviving a violent showdown, a conniving teen breaks out of a hospital determined to wreak havoc on her father's new wife and family.

Title: Trap City
Description: A rapper caught in the drug trade becomes an overnight sensation with a viral hit song. Facing prison, he must choose between his rising fame and testifying against a dangerous criminal.

Title: Treasure Trackers
Description: A trio of misfit middle schoolers band together to investigate their small town's mythic treasure, only to uncover a Halloween curse.

Title: Finalement
Description: Lawyer suffering from a condition preventing him from lying takes a cross-country road trip in France. Musical fantasy blending trumpet and piano. Original Ibrahim Maalouf soundtrack.

Title: Ilana Glazer: Human Magic
Description: Explores Ilana Glazer's high school experiences, tackling life's realities, and her journey as an unconventional mother who uses marijuana.

Title: Bob Mackie: Naked Illusion
Description: Bob Mackie, a six-decade costume designer, received a Lifetime Achievement award and Tony nomination for The Cher Show. His unique, unfiltered style has been showcased in a new documentary.

Title: Air War
Description: Rivalry between Israeli fighter pilots escalates before 1967 Six-Day War. As Israel's survival is threatened, they must unite to lead their squadron, ultimately achieving victory.

Title: A Journey
Description: Refusing treatment for her cancer, a woman goes on a road trip across Tasmania to check off items on her bucket list with her husband and best friend.

Title: Lost City
Description: It tells the unknown story of the Amsterdam city tram that collaborated with the Nazis and deported tens of thousands of Jews to the train stations on their way to the death camps. We experience their last tram ride.

Title: Group Therapy
Description: A witty exploration of mental health challenges through relatable conversations, striking a balance between depth and levity.

Title: Uyir Thamizhukku
Description: Conspiracy and betrayals engulf veteran politician. Challenged to unravel truth, protect career and reputation. Employing intellect and allies, secrets emerge as he pursues justice, overcoming obstacles in this riveting political thriller.

Title: Can't Feel Nothing
Description: Examines the connection between internet use and emotional disorders.

Title: Friendly Fire
Description: Sonya , a female CEO wants to put Philippine esports on the map. She scouts a young female player Hazel from a internet cafe, sees the potential in her and trains her.

Title: The Adamant Girl
Description: Meena, who loves a man from a lower caste but her family thinks she is possessed and cast the spell out of her.

Title: The Ring
Description: Arnon Noble is a religious man with a strong bond to his mother, a Holocaust survivor. When the mother's health deteriorates, he travels to her old hometown, Budapest to search for the mythological ring that saved her life in the past.

Title: Sucha Soorma
Description: A 100+ year-old story of the legendary rebel, the famous Punjab da Kissa, Sucha Soorma!

Title: Go Against the Flow
Description: Second half of the 1970s. Several teenagers from Ustrzyki Dolne, led by a charismatic and undisciplined student of the Ustrzyki vocational school, Siczka, decided to become punks and play punk rock. They were inspired by the Sex Pistols band heard on a foreign radio station and the new "punk" culture. First, they send a letter to Radio Free Europe asking for more "free people's music" on the air. To their amazement, the letter is read live, and the station starts airing a weekly punk show. Of course, neither Siczka nor the rest of the boys have any idea what a big deal this modest show will start and what great dark powers will come against them. The letter read out in Free Europe was noticed by representatives of the repressive apparatus of the People's Republic of Poland. The SB officer, Jerzy Majak, while interrogating Siczka, makes it clear that Ustrzyki Dolne is not London and there will be no "punk" in his commune.

Title: Ingu Mirugangal Vaazhum Idam
Description: John works in the Security Guard Office and is single-handedly raising his only daughter, Jenny. Genie, who has an inordinate affection for her father, looks after John. However, her boyfriend, rapes and murders Jenny along with his friend

Title: Lady Outlaw
Description: In 1890s Oklahoma, a pair of fugitive lovers face a perilous journey home. With lawmen and bounty hunters hot on their heels, George and Rose must outwit their pursuers and navigate treacherous terrain to reach safety in Ingalls.

Title: Lafran
Description: A biopic film, Lafran Pane in building the Islamic Students Association (HMI). The national and Islamic values instilled by Lafran became the foundation for HMI in contributing to Indonesia.

Title: Queens of Drama
Description: Pop diva Mimi Madamour's career peaks in 2005 before spiraling downwards due to her tumultuous love affair with punk icon Billie Kohler, their passionate and rage-fueled relationship playing out on stage for half a century.

Title: Kuramerukagari
Description: Kagari is a girl who runs a mapmaking business focused on recording an ever-changing, labyrinth-like town. Watch to see how her daily life unfolds.

Title: Return to Wickensburg
Description: Mr. Hexenmeister has escaped from prison, and once again threatens Wickensburg. It's a race against time to find an ancient orb, capable of destroying the entire town, before it falls into the wrong hands.

Title: Vicious Murder
Description: With his crypto empire on the brink, a businessman conspires to murder his wife and steal her fortune but uncovers a web of deception in the process.

Title: Vive e Deixa Andar
Description: A clumsy lonely orphan, Lucas is a moving target for all kinds of misfortunes. Spending a weekend in a mansion he will cause damage, discover secrets from his past and find love. A dangerous-romantic action comedy, with a license to laugh.

Title: Father-in-law and Son-in-law
Description: Park Jin-gi, a third-rate movie star is now out of fashion. Do-pil, a third-rate singer whose goal is to produce an album, and Jin-gi, whose goal is to produce a movie, were just trying to do well in Busan, where they left to find investors, but the results were a mess. In the end, Jin-gi, who was kicked out of the house, begins to live together with his father-in-law, who suffers from dementia due to his mother-in-law's scheme and is mentally unstable and constantly has accidents.

Title: Ruslaan
Description: The unstoppable force Ruslaan, is coming to break free of the chains of conformity. With his gun and guitar, he's about to create a symphony of rebellion like no other.

Title: Diplodocus
Description: The titular dinosaur goes on an adventure to save his parents who have disappeared under mysterious circumstances. Alongside a wizard and two quirky scientists, he encounters fantastical creatures and amazing places along the way.

Title: Hahacar
Description: Hahacar is a situational suspense comedy film that takes you on a ride filled with chaos and drama packed into one night's story.

Title: The Contract
Description: A married couple enters into a contract to have a threesome and realizes what is most important to their marrage.

Title: Throuple
Description: Ysay and Hannah, who were in a Throuple relationship, find themselves searching for a new partner after losing their boyfriend. Will they find the perfect third piece?

Title: If That Mockingbird Don't Sing
Description: After a brutal dumping, 17-year-old Sydnie realizes she is pregnant. She decides to use it as a chance to get her ex back and give her life direction but soon realizes it won't be the quick fix she had hoped for.

Title: Wanda Rutkiewicz. Ostatnia wyprawa
Description: The true story of Wanda Rutkiewicz, the first woman in the world and the first person from Poland to climb the highest peaks on earth - told by herself. Wanda entered the men's world of high-mountain expeditions without an invitation and paid the highest price for it. The film's director, herself a mountaineer, sets off to the Himalayas in Wanda's footsteps. The clue to the search is the heroine's audio diary found among a pile of archival materials.

Title: Cara
Description: Cara, a mentally troubled woman escaped from an institution, believes in a conspiracy against her. She plans horrific acts using her show's viewers, exploring mental health, abuse, and violence, leaving a disturbing trail.

Title: Visceral
Description: A chronicle of a crime of passion, takes an unexpected turn. A young marriage in crisis, find themselves dragged into a world of police corruption, money laundering, and a long-ago-orchestrated revenge.

Title: Breaking and Re-entering
Description: An invincible theft group led by Chang Bojun, who secretly carried out a 1 billion yuan theft case on New Year's Eve. Unexpectedly, they encountered a gang robbing gang, and Chang's ex-girlfriend was accidentally involved in the case.

Title: Sacrum Vindictae II
Description: Nathaniel Nucci thought his brutal hit-man days were behind him, until unseemly betrayed by one of his own military brothers. The story dives deep into the underbelly and ugliness of corruption, greed and murder associated with organized crime.

Title: The Path
Description: A young woman returns to her childhood home to discover strange circumstances surrounding her parents death and the town that she grew up in.

Title: Teasing Master Takagi-san Movie
Description: Takagi, now grown up, revisits her middle school as a trainer. She encounters Nishikata, her former classmate she used to tease, now a PE teacher there. Their playful dynamic resumes, leading to more interactions between the two.

Title: Adios Amigo
Description: At a bustling bus stand, two men from contrasting social strata cross paths. One basks in affluence, the other grapples with life's challenges. Together, they embark on a journey laced with humor and unexpected adventures.

Title: Murphy
Description: Ordinary guy David's life takes an extraordinary turn after interacting with his late grandfather's peculiar radio.

Title: Fasel Men El Lahazat El Lazeeza
Description: A romantic comedy about a couple who encounter many problems, until a portal opens by chance that leads them to parallel worlds.

Title: Huwad
Description: When Romina learns that her husband has been cheating on her, she turns to the town's folk healer for help and obtains a love potion. But it seems the potion is working on everyone except her husband.

Title: La Grande
Description: The career of Dominican Merengue Típico singer Fefita La Grande.

Title: First Do No Pharm
Description: We have had too much medicine for too many years. The time to act is now. How one doctor's fight against corporate greed led to an ancient, life-changing solution for heart disease.

Insecure plus-sized event planner Sayra falls for Tahsir. Confronting past trauma, her self-esteem falters. She embraces self-love, respect, and societal acceptance, redefining beauty standards, overcoming struggles with body image.

Title: Khwaabon Ka Jhamela
Description: Zubin, rejected by his fiancee Shehnaz due to bedroom woes, travels to UK. There, he meets Ruby, an intimacy coordinator. They strike an unusual deal, embarking on a comical journey of self-discovery and personal growth.

Title: Twin Lies
Description: When a young barista takes her twin sister's place for an escorting gig, all hell breaks loose when their mysterious client turns dangerous.

Title: Devil
Description: Hema married to Alex meets Arun in accident, bond grows. Will Proximity causes strain on Hema's relationship with Alex.

Title: Twiggy
Description: UK model and cultural icon Twiggy, real name Lesley Lawson, whose career kickstarted in the 1960s.

Title: The Property
Description: Regina and her granddaughter Mika embark on a journey to Poland to reclaim their family property seized during World War II. But their quest quickly unravels. Regina unexpectedly decides to abandon the mission entirely, leaving Mika lost and confused. To complicate matters further, an irritating distant relative keeps appearing at every turn. Just as Mika finds herself falling for a charming tour guide, Regina seizes the opportunity to pursue her own hidden agenda: finding her long-lost love, from whom she was separated seventy years ago.

Title: I Left My Heart in Colombia
Description: Two friends are brought to Medellin, Colombia under the guise of a pleasurable business trip by their friend who is already there to make good on a financial obligation. The man that they are all forced to meet with to settle the debt has something special planned for ALL OF THEM.

Title: Sugar Mami
Description: Giovanni and his wife, Vanessa are the perfect couple. That is until one day when Giovanni meets a beautiful woman named Mia who starts obsessing over him, and things slowly take a turn for the worse.

Title: Heather
Description: A philanderer is lured into a kinky encounter by a provocative woman, only to discover she has undergone gender reassignment and was once the boy he terrorized in high school.

Title: Fortunes of War
Description: A small team of British commandos are cut off from their comrades following a raid in Normandy.

Title: Sensei no Shiroi Uso
Description: Turn a blind eye or lie to avoid getting hurt. If you don't do that, you won't be able to live...

Title: Being Blanche Houellebecq
Description: Michel Houellebecq travels to Guadeloupe to take part in a look-alike contest, whose jury is chaired by Blanche Gardin. Unforeseen events will plunge the duo into the heart of a bizarre intrigue.

Title: Yo Yo Honey Singh: Famous
Description: Dive deep into Yo Yo Honey Singh's sudden disappearance at the peak of his career.

Title: Oculus
Description: Zia Lainey, shattered by the loss of her son, awakens inside the afterlife of the Oculus, transforming her into Zylah, Leader of the Suits. As she navigates this enigmatic realm, Zylah grapples with her new-found identity and revenge to hold those who are responsible. All while seeking solace and understanding for her own grief.

Title: Unnatural
Description: A gunslinger on a mission from God must track down supernatural creatures as penance for his past sins.

Title: Heart of a Servant: The Father Flanagan Story
Description: Father Flanagan's mission work, struggles, challenges and passion in reforming juvenile justice systems and youth care for troubled/disadvantaged youth are depicted, showing his impact on America's approach to these issues.

Title: (Un)lucky Sisters
Description: After their father's death, estranged sisters stumble upon his hidden fortune, forcing them to decide whether to keep the money or do the right thing.

Title: A Family Affair
Description: Owners of a spiritual retreat risk losing property. Auction interrupts anniversary event. Misunderstandings with younger date and buyers occur. Family conflicts arise as they try to prevent foreclosure.

Title: First Nights at Freddy's
Description: Before the events of the original FNaF Musical, several stories come together to uncover Fazbear Entertainment's web of lies.

Title: The Uncivil War: America Divided
Description: In the year 2020, in a country that seemed to hate itself, what chance did two childhood friends, one white and one black, from opposite sides of the political spectrum stand at remaining friends? What chance did any of us have?

Title: To the Moon
Description: After a chance encounter with a handsome stranger, single dad Sam wrestles with the idea of coming out of the closet at 38.

Title: Reinas
Description: Two teenage sisters are about to leave their country forever when they unexpectedly reconnect with an absent father. This relationship will both amplify and ease their pain of change.

Title: Kardes Takimi
Description: The story follows a family with kids and parents that are agents. One day the parents tell the kids that they will be away for 2 days. When the parents arrive they get trapped. The kids find a robot and they go on a adventurous journey.

Title: Bastar: The Naxal Story
Description: Based on the real-life incidents of Naxals in Chattisgarh - The Bastar rebellion broke out in 1910 in present day Chattisgarh.

Title: Reversi
Description: A man's undying love for his wife and son makes him go to great lengths to correct his past for a better future.

Title: Bohurupi
Description: An itinerant showman, who amuses people and earns money by impersonating demons, undergoes a psychological transformation after having a miraculous dream.

Title: Salitan
Description: A wife suspects her husband of infidelity during a trip to Bali. She meets an attractive stranger who stirs unfaithful feelings within her. She contemplates encouraging her husband's unfaithfulness to reduce her guilt.

Title: La damnée
Description: Yara, 25, a young Moroccan woman who has come to study in Paris, has not left her home for several months. Agoraphobic since childhood, she survives, cloistered, locked in between her nightmares.

Title: The Shelter
Description: On a solo hike, a woman finds herself stalked by a bear. Only one will survive.

Title: María, Me Muero
Description: Maria's hypochondriac husband believes every cold is terminal. After enduring his antics, Maria takes matters into her own hands to address his irrational fear of death.

Title: The Slave and the Sorcerer
Description: Slave Tyrol leads a quest to rescue Princess Meyra from evil wizard Akaris' fortress. Facing ancient creatures and tests, he must slay a dragon to save the princess and realm from darkness.

Title: The 3_2 Pulldown
Description: A filmmaker and a political activist from the future join forces to exploit art for propaganda, but their alliance quickly turns into a power struggle that threatens the very foundation of creativity.

Title: Sunce nikad vise
Description: Vid, a father grappling with the encroaching threat of a multicorporate iron ore mine near his home, discovers resilience and hope through his young son's imaginative perspective, blending optimism, fairy tales, and mysticism into their grim reality.

Title: Dickweed
Description: Two people got kidnapped. One man lost his dick. No-one got any money. This heist-gone-horribly-wrong led one Newport Beach detective on an international manhunt for the most twisted criminal he'd ever hunted.

Title: Un lío de millones
Description: In a village in the Sierra de Madrid, a couple feels that their children, who have since moved out, have forgotten about them. To get them back, they will pretend that they have won the lottery and that they are multimillionaires.

Title: Vampire Lake
Description: A girl journeys to a secluded lake to summon a vampire.

Title: This Is Benjamin Ingrosso: Part 1
Description: This is Benjamin Ingrosso follows Benjamin from his early years as a child star to his current pursuit, of becoming Sweden's first international pop star.

Title: Right Here, Right Now
Description: One fateful night, the divergent paths of four high school students intersect, and as they navigate the moment's urgency, they are forced to confront their inner struggles and redefine their identities.

Title: Futon
Description: Tokio Takenaka (48) is a scriptwriter who's lost his passion for his work, and whose relationship with his wife Madoka (37) has turned sour. He spends his days lost in a haze. One day, a girl named Yoshimi Yokoyama (21) barges into his office, saying that she's a huge fan of his work and aiming to be a scriptwriter herself. Overcome by her enthusiasm, he agrees to take her in. As they work together, he begins to sense her talent as a writer, and at the same time, comes to feel sexually attracted towards her. Soon he's writing scripts that he's proud of again, and begins to feel fulfilled in both his private and work lives. But it doesn't take long before he learns about her boyfriend and fellow scriptwriter Hideo Tanaka (20). He becomes madly jealous, but.

Title: Sugar Island
Description: The story of a pregnant 14-year-old girl living in a Dominican sugar plantation.

Title: Cheat
Description: Zoe's deteriorating marriage leaves her feeling isolated and longing for connection in the aftermath of a personal trauma. To escape loneliness, she blindly stumbles into a passionate affair, which ultimately leads her down a deadly path.

Title: Barbie & Kendra Crash Joe Bob's Drive-In Jamboree
Description: Barbie and Kendra race to save Joe Bob Briggs' drive-in from a land baron's plans for a golf course while professing their love for Joe Bob and his sidekick, hoping to catch a terrible movie in the process.

Title: Dolly Parton: Bigger Hair, Bigger Heart
Description: No royal beginnings for this Queen of Country Music. Known for her larger-than-life positive attitude parading big hair and bold make-up, Dolly Parton would carved out her own identity as a singer, movie actress, and entrepreneur.

Title: One Million Babes BC
Description: It is the 3rd setting of the bright orange orb in the sky. Ogg, the leader of a wildly band of prehistoric people have chosen Nila to be sacrificed in order to appease sky Gods.

Title: Maharaaj
Description: Cook unexpectedly enters dysfunctional couple's life, transforms their lifestyle. Enigmatic circumstances lead to cook's abrupt departure. Trio's peculiar dynamic leaves unanswered questions about their future.

Title: Her Drunken Diary
Description: A young wife battles alcoholism while raising a child amid tension with her overbearing mother-in-law, straining her marriage and self-esteem.

Title: Keanu Reeves: The One and Only
Description: The story of Keanu Reeves, from a turbulent upbringing to becoming not only one of the most beloved actors in the world, but also one of the most beloved people.

Title: Mayavanam
Description: Four medical school friends hike into remote backcountry, hoping for adventure, but soon find themselves in a desperate fight for survival, encountering one crisis after another.

Title: Fit for Murder
Description: Based on actual events, The lives of fitness celebrities Craig Titus and Kelly Ryan took a dark turn when they hired a young female assistant.

Title: Panchavalsarapadhathi
Description: Revolves around Sanoj who runs the Akshaya Centre in Kalamberi village. All of a sudden, Kalambasura -a local legend- starts appearing infront of the villagers.

Title: ¿Es el enemigo? La película de Gila
Description: In 1936, in Madrid, a young man named Miguel Gila lives a peaceful life with his grandparents in a simple attic. However, the outbreak of the Civil War changes his destiny.

Title: Rocket Driver
Description: An autorickshaw driver frequently expresses discontent with life's aspects but harbors an ambitious dream of changing the world, though his actions fail to align with his aspirations.

Title: Manipula
Description: Sylvia, a resolute CIB officer, seeks revenge for her father's death and confronts Armando, her main target.

Title: Homegrown
Description: Three Trump supporters from different backgrounds unite to campaign across America in 2020, advocating for his re-election while laying foundations for what they hope will be a long-lasting political movement.

Title: Leonard Cohen: If It Be Your Will
Description: A cinematic celebration of Leonard Cohen's music, life, and legacy through the eyes of his son Adam and tribute performances by musical icons.

Title: Death & Taxes
Description: An exploration of a wealthy man's obsessive refusal to pay taxes, serving as a case study on the costlier ramifications of America's tax benefits for the rich.

Title: Tiempo de Pagar
Description: Richard, an Argentinian money exchanger who works at the Buenos Aires downtown, finds himself involved in a series of problems that lead him to a thrilling race against the clock.

Title: Ai no nukumori
Description: Due to an unexpected event, a man and a woman, end up switching bodies. Despite coming from completely different backgrounds and environments, both try to overcome the various difficulties that arise from their body swap.

Title: Effigy
Description: Isolated on the fringes of a soulless metropolis, Catherine survives on scraps of translation work. But a mysterious client offers a lucrative job, and an opportunity for Catherine to indulge in her malformed and incompatible desires.

Title: The Town Without Halloween
Description: In a town immersed in Halloween traditions, a group of teens stumbles upon the Mayor's scheme to abolish the beloved holiday. With dark powers at stake, they must save their community and Halloween itself in The Town Without Halloween.

Title: 13th Summer
Description: During their annual vacation at an isolated beach, Ben and Vee unexpectedly encounter a mysterious backpacker who draws them into a twisted web of lies, deceit and ultimately, revenge.

Title: The Man Who Loved UFOs
Description: Argentina, 1986. Journalist José de Zer and his cameraman travel to Córdoba after an odd proposal. At a burnt patch in the hills, they depict an alleged alien presence for their news show through increasingly bizarre staged scenes.

Title: Nature of the Crime
Description: After decades in prison, three men navigate the complex bureaucracy of the parole system and deal with its psychological toll.

Title: Kingdom Reign
Description: Set amidst the crack epidemic of the 1980s, the narrative delves into themes of betrayal and legacy as a former Marine is forced to inherit a drug empire his father built.

Title: Elephant Steps
Description: After fire wrecks African village, Yaya's enslaved for cocoa. UN agent and US scientist unite to reveal child slavery in chocolate industry, battling demons.

Title: Woodbridge
Description: Four teenagers sneak out of their houses one night and walk across town to confront the school bully, who happens to be looking for them as well.

Title: Phil Herman's Unearthed
Description: This anthology intricately interlaces four compelling tales, each orbiting individuals who unravel hidden, lost, or long-guarded secrets. Brace yourself for an exhilarating odyssey of discovery and suspense as "Unearthed" plunges deep beneath the surface to unveil mysteries concealed for far too long.

Title: Ripper Revealed
Description: When Edward Taylor, a seasoned journalist, interviews a famous ripperologist he uncovers more than just Jack the ripper's identity.

Title: Camp Blood 9: Bride of Blood
Description: A group of misfit rockers rents an Airbnb on the way to a festival, with no idea that they've booked an eternal stay in Camp Blood. The Killer Clown is back, and this time he's taking a bride.

Title: Our Lovely Pig Slaughter
Description: Karel and his family gather yearly for a pig-killing tradition, where amidst celebrations, underlying tensions and secrets surface, leading to a chaotic event that forces Karel to confront harsh realities.

Title: Santa's Cousin
Description: Santa Claus sends his reluctant cousin Colton on a mission to bring holiday cheer to a small New Mexico town in jeopardy.

Title: Kahan Shuru Kahan Khatam
Description: A commitment-phobic woman refuses to marry the man her parents have chosen for her. Chaos ensues as she tries to escape the wedding while the groom and his family chase her down, leading to a hilarious and cringe-worthy comedy of errors.

Title: Out
Description: Lovers Tom and Ajani dream of a new life in which their relationship does not have to be a secret. The two feel like outsiders in their conservative, small village. They move to Amsterdam, where a journey of self-discovery awaits them.

Title: Kolpaçino: 4 4'lük
Description: Two rivals meet to settle old scores in a casino but things are interrupted by a raid.

Title: Z Zone
Description: A group of young delinquents, transferred to a remote military base for rehabilitation, find themselves caught in a web of secrets and battling sinister forces lurking in the shadows.

Title: Jhamkudi
Description: Raniwada, a village in Gujarat, is cursed by an evil witch named JHAMKUDI during Navratri celebrations. Real estate agent Bablo and royal family heir Kumud return to face the witch's wrath and save Raniwada.

Title: Erbsünde - Veil of Sin
Description: Searching for an adventurous story in the woods, a group of journalism students awaken a superhuman being from its lost cryo-chamber. A long night of man hunting and desperation ensues.

Title: Fortune Feimster: Crushing It
Description: Feimster humorously recounts her marital experiences, personal growth, and the comedic aspects of daily life, offering a relatable and entertaining perspective.

Title: Thekku Vadakku
Description: Two rivals, a retired engineer and rice mill owner, engage in a fierce competition. Their feud entertains the town as they battle to determine the ultimate victor and whether the loser accepts defeat gracefully.

Title: The Three Michaels
Description: Three young Michael Jackson impersonators travel to Hollywood in search of the American Dream just as their idol's darker past is about to be exposed.

Title: Mong Vuot
Description: 911 operator Pamela's daughter is kidnapped, forcing her and estranged husband Jeremy, a police officer, to follow the kidnapper's demands to ensure her safe return.

Title: Isang himala
Description: Elsa, a simple woman from a rural barrio, becomes a beacon of hope and controversy when, after hearing a divine calling during an eclipse, she is believed to have the power to heal, transforming her village into a pilgrimage site and challenging the faith, relationships, and beliefs of everyone around her.

Title: The Deserving
Description: A depressed mute serial killer tormented in his house by the ghost of his victims. On the morning he's set to kill himself he's visited by a sudden walk-in client in need of a photo shoot.

Title: L'homme aux mille visages
Description: A conman juggles four different identities, each with a distinct personality, while living with four women simultaneously. An investigator uncovers his fraud by delving into his shifting personas through first-hand investigation.

Title: Honey Money Phony
Description: A working girl accidentally incurs a massive debt. She crosses paths with a con man. Amidst lies and deceit, they navigate a tumultuous journey, questioning their paths in life.

Title: Nayanthara: Beyond the Fairy Tale
Description: The love story of South Indian superstar Nayanthara, who recently got married in a fairytale wedding to filmmaker Vignesh Shivan.

Title: Look at Me
Description: A fictional autobiography about an insecure, awkward and lonely actor who goes on an unwitting journey of self-love in the midst of an eating disorder relapse.

Title: Maa Nanna Superhero
Description: Johnny embarks on a mission to help his adoptive father, inadvertently reuniting with his biological father Prakash, who was forced to abandon him years ago but now seeks reconciliation.

Title: Simon Says
Description: Simon Says is a thriller about a traumatized (PTSD) college-graduated young man who moved to Hollywood to pursue his acting career and face the reality of the movie industry business.

Title: Interstate
Description: A supernatural thriller in which a hitman, facing an existential crisis, decides to exit the game and leave town with the woman he loves, but his plans are disrupted by a mysterious young man and his ruthless former boss.

Title: Customs Frontline
Description: Hong Kong customs officers discover illegal weapons on a cargo ship and trace them back to an international conflict. Elite agents go undercover, uncovering a transnational operation with roots closer to home.

Title: Glass Casa
Description: Jamie's plans for a relaxed bachelorette party with her three closest gals turn nightmarish when the celebration takes a dark twist: an unexpected guest is discovered mysteriously murdered.

Title: Séance
Description: In 1892 California, a Victorian woman contemplating adultery is forced to take refuge from a storm at the home of her first husband and his unstable wife, who claims to be haunted by their dead child.

Title: Bad Boyz
Description: A directionless schoolboy becomes a goon to impress a girl fascinated by local goons. His decision leads to suspenseful, humorous consequences in the thrilling crime world.

Title: Yolki 11
Description: Uncle Yura, serves as a security guard in an elite village, raises a mini-pig Kostya and does not like New Year at all.

Title: Zamora
Description: The 1960s. Walter Vismara is a thirty-year-old man who works as an accountant in a small factory in Vigevano. When the company he works for closes without warning, Walter finds a new job at another company in the bustling city of Milan.

Title: Men of War
Description: A former U.S. Green Beret is recruited to remove Venezuela's president and after the mission fails, he is pursued by the government he faithfully served.

Title: Appudo Ippudo Eppudo
Description: A wayward young man becomes involved in a criminal conspiracy.

Title: Kozhipannai Chelladurai
Description: Chelladurai and Jeyasudha, siblings, face life's struggles after a devastating tragedy, their unbreakable bond fortified by their uncle Periyasamy's constant guidance since childhood.

Title: Naked Nations - Tribe Hong Kong
Description: A group of homosexuals going through the harsh quarantine measured in Hong Kong.

Title: The Phantom Warrior
Description: The origin story of masked vigilante and immortal soul, Nemesis Knight.

Title: A Widow Seduced
Description: A career-driven widow falls for a charming businessman that she meets online, only to discover that her new beau has a deadly secret.

Title: Naach Ga Ghuma
Description: Follows the lively duo - the woman of the house and the house help, and how their love-hate relationship unfolds in a humorous drama.

Title: A Girl Like Him
Description: A Girl Like Him is a coming of age drama centered around a small-town teen who makes a surprising life change, spiraling their lifelong best friend into a dark place when he realizes things will never be the same between them.

Title: Bocchi the Rock! Re:
Description: Introverted girl, skilled guitarist 'Guitar Hero', dreams of school band. Unable to make friends until high school when drummer contacts her, altering her solitary life.

Title: They Turned Us Into Killers
Description: Karma is assaulted by her boyfriend, BJ, which leads to her committing suicide. Star hunts down BJ and his brothers, and begins to torture them, while reading to them Karma's suicide letter, before taking each of their lives.

Title: Black Heat
Description: One night, two parents, out of options, infiltrate a top level drug dealer/pimp's apartment complex to rescue their teenage daughter.

Title: Nocturnes
Description: Amidst the lush Eastern Himalayan forests, moths convey a mysterious message. Under the cover of night, two inquisitive observers illuminate this clandestine universe, unraveling the secrets whispered by these enigmatic creatures.

Title: ¿Quién es quién?
Description: Valentina, make a wish for her 9th birthday. The next day, all the members of his family wake up with the body exchanged. Chaos grips the family and they wonder: Who is who?

Title: La petite vadrouille
Description: Justine, her husband and their gang of friends come up with a solution to their money problems: organize a fake romantic cruise for Franck, a major investor, who is looking to seduce a woman.

Title: Agapouse ta louloudia perissotero
Description: Three brothers build an unusual time-machine in order to bring their long-dead mother back to life.

Title: Miss Cleo: Her Rise and Fall
Description: Miss Cleo, a psychic reader, achieves fame through Psychic Readers Network in the 90s. However, the network gets accused of fraud and misleading advertising, turning her world upside down.

Title: Blackout
Description: The streets of Pune, where a single night of darkness engulfs the city in mystery, as crime reporter Lenny, gets entangled in a web of greed and misfortune.

Title: Ek Anjaan Rishtey Ka Guilt 3
Description: Akshay, a charismatic Casanova, has an illicit affair with his boss' wife, Ayesha, but life takes an unexpected turn when Akshay and Ayesha's step-daughter, Kriti, fall in love. Will purity of LOVE win over desires of LUST?

Title: Protocol-7
Description: With the catastrophic regression of her adopted son, Lexi, a small-town lawyer, is confronted with the reality of corporate fraud at the highest level. Will she hold a massive corporation accountable in this true whistleblower story?

Title: Deadly Triangles
Description: When a childless couple takes in a pregnant woman, their peaceful life is upended by temptation. Meanwhile, a sexually fluid medical agent entangles a couple in a daring game of seduction and desire.

Title: Agents
Description: When a priceless artifact is stolen, two agents team up to retrieve it from a wealthy criminal mastermind. With everything against them, they'll take the explosive action to the land, sea, and air.

Title: The Night Curse of Reatrei
Description: After Pol Pot regime, 1993, they moved into an abandoned orphanage. They realized that the whole building was cursed by a vengeful spirit, Reatrei. Tragedies start to happen one after another until they find what her curse wants.

Title: Unspoken
Description: Follows a closeted teenager in a religious community who finds a love letter written to his grandfather by another man, so he sets out to find the person.

Title: Cookster: The Darkest Days
Description: A dyslexic teen misunderstood by his family and desperate for respect, becomes a drug dealer struggling with addiction and debt while a rival threatens to destroy his world, driving him apart from the woman he loves.

Title: Delivery Boy
Description: Small-time real estate agents Bhau and Chochya encounter Dr. Amruta Deshmukh, who aims to establish a surrogacy hospital. Their journey to make her vision a reality unfolds.

Title: Books & Drinks
Description: David travels to Dominican Republic to sell a house he has inherited from the father he never knew. There he will meet Maria, who is going to turn his life upside down.

Title: Reloaded 2
Description: In a dystopian future where criminals take over, detective Jimmy Cloud gets a deadly case around a kidnapping carried out by a brutal crime syndicate.

Title: The Life and Deaths of Christopher Lee
Description: Follows fresh interviews, archival footage, and various animation techniques like marionation to recreate one of the world's leading actors on screen, bringing them back to life through innovative methods.

Title: Nearing Death
Description: Torment near death that is difficult to ward off with prayer terrorizes a family. What sin did they commit?

Title: I Want to Be Neenja! The Movie
Description: GoGirl is on a mission to spread smiles. She's a superhero with a Barbie Jeep, and her path to spreading smiles is halted by gamer-billionaire Chow, also a real ninja; so Girl must embark on her own journey to ninja-hood to take Chow down.

Title: Men Are from QC, Women Are from Alabang
Description: Two lovers navigate post-graduation life, facing challenges of long-distance relationship and career demands. Their perspectives on shared experiences diverge as physical and emotional distance grows, straining their bond over time.

Title: One by One
Description: Follows David Rosenau's journey from funeral director to prison guard, undercover detective, and homicide investigator before a calling to become a pastor after a life-threatening injury, impacting lives for eternity.

Title: Takas
Description: Best friends, Angel and Lexi, run away after committing a crime. Their seemingly quiet life becomes messy when a new man enters the picture.

Title: Woman with the Red Lipstick
Description: Looking to spice things up, Lucy and her boyfriend assume fake names and roleplay meeting for the first time in a bar. A few days later Lucy sees a news report about a missing persons case where the victim has the same name she just used.

Title: Tide
Description: Four friends race against the tide in a bay famous for its quicksands, but a lurking threat will aggravate the situation.

Title: Pombalai Orumai
Description: During COVID, Ancymol, a Junior Health Inspector, is transferred to a rural village. She meets Sunitha, a tailor seeking help with an investigation. Together, they unravel the mystery with the help of Ancymol's friends.

Title: Yakuza Girl
Description: Detectives investigate bizarre murders connected to the Yakuza mob and a covert ninja assassin.

Title: My First Girl Crush
Description: Ingrid, a shy teen, juggles the pressures of high school and her conservative Chinese-Australian family after falling for her best friend, Stella.

Title: My Everything
Description: Follows Mona, a woman in her 60's who is at a point in her life where she wants to start caring for herself. But when her disabled son is unexpectedly having a baby, she has another responsibility to deal with.

Title: Anchakkallakokkan
Description: In a small country town a cowardly police constable must survive his first days of duty when a convicted felon in lock up tries to seek revenge.

Title: Bag of Lies
Description: Desperate to save his dying wife, Matt turns to The Bag, an ancient relic with dark magic. The cure demands a chilling ritual and strict rules. As his wife heals, Matt's sanity unravels, facing terrifying consequences.

Title: The Shameless
Description: After killing a cop in a Delhi brothel, Renuka takes refuge in a northern India community of sex workers. There, she begins a forbidden romance with the 17-year-old Devika. Against all odds, they try to forge their path to freedom.

Title: He Loves Me Not
Description: An aspiring actress chosen as a wild card for a reality TV dating show uses a secret elixir to win the heart of the star, but when her deception is revealed, she discovers a messy but real chance for love.

Title: The Best Laid Plans
Description: Resa schemes with a gardener to disinherit her fiance's daughter, while Glen's revenge plot against his father takes a dark turn as his seduction of his stepmother and her sister leads to a shocking, life-altering twist.

Title: #AAY
Description: When a man comes home between covid lockdowns, he connects with old friends and falls for a woman who feels influenced by her caste, while finding love.

Title: Slaughterhouse on the Hill
Description: After attending the homecoming football game, a night of terror ensues when a group of friends party at an abandoned slaughterhouse.

Title: Mirza: Part 1 - Joker
Description: Mirza is a Gangster, born just to break the rules, being investigated by the local police, CBI. The action-packed movie will have plenty of surprises. Ankush Hazra Fast Products Film.

Title: Our Blue World: A Water Odyssey
Description: Water cycles disrupted by climate change spark droughts, floods, biodiversity loss. Combining ancestral wisdom and modern science offers solutions. Explores visionary relationships with water, inspiring positive change.

Title: Or Utopia
Description: Japan, 2024. The Earth is dominated by a mysteriously giant creature (That Thing) and the group of 12 survivors has formed an uneasy community out of necessity to survive Two years later, Hirayama, the hotel owner, is found dead.

Title: House of Ga'a
Description: A ruthless Prime Minister desperate for revenge ferociously rises to power, stopping at nothing to become more powerful than the kings he served.

Title: Kacher Manush Dure Thuiya
Description: Follows couple in long-distance relationship across thousands of miles. Distance strains the relationship, causing pain, doubt, mistrust, anger, resentment. Ultimately leads to separation before emotional reunion.

Title: Thine Ears Shall Bleed
Description: In 1860s America, a minister's family hears an unexplained noise from woods during their wagon journey. Mistaking it for divine presence, they worship until realizing its sinister nature.

Title: Kiss of the Con Queen
Description: A striving actor is targeted by an ingenious and sadistic scammer, terrorizing the industry, impersonating Hollywood elites.

Title: Power
Description: Driven to contain threats to social order, American policing has exploded in scope and scale over hundreds of years. Now, it can be described by one word: power.

Title: Worlds Apart
Description: Makio Kodai, a shy 35-year-old novelist, takes in her 15-year-old niece Asa Takumi after Asa's parents die in a car accident. Despite Makio's difficulties with relationships, she and Asa begin living together, forming a bond.

Title: Here We Go
Description: Those Chinese four-character proverbs in our daily lives, and express Chinese people's compromise while facing problems. Would this "Lai dou lai le" (meaning: now that we've here) attitude solve problems, or drag us into further abyss?

Title: It's All Over: The Kiss That Changed Spanish Football
Description: Spanish footballers come together for the first time to relive the turbulent 2023 Women's World Cup and the kiss that overshadowed their victory.

Title: Neon Fear
Description: The year is 2049. Android-Jason-Replicants are being used to hunt humans. To save ourselves we must use a time machine to travel back to 1984, and awaken the one person with the power to stop them all - the REAL JASON.

Title: Bye Bye Boredom
Description: 13-year-old Jackie and her friend Nova test their limits among horses, drugs and EPA tractors in a rural village.

Title: Playtime
Description: Influencer Allyson, bride-to-be Roni, and newly single Patricia are from different worlds, unaware that trusting the wrong man will force them into a terrifying situation where their lives may depend on each other.

Title: Game On
Description: When a hyper dimensional crack arises between our reality and the game world, the best gaming players in the Netherlands must enter the game world to save their country.

Title: Blended Christmas
Description: A newlywed bride's honeymoon plans get derailed when she takes in her husband's ex-wife and kids, with an angel's guidance helping them become a family.

Title: Flesh of the Unforgiven
Description: A dark, psychological, supernatural horror that follows a struggling couple tortured by the twisted games played by the Death Dealer and his manipulating legion of demons.

Title: Mustafa
Description: The childhood of Mustafa Kemal Atatürk, the founder of the Republic of Turkey

Title: Carol
Description: Self-centered Solomon Lynch takes a journey through his past, present, and future. But it takes more than Christmas spirit to set things right in this story of hope, faith, and redemption.

Title: The Only Child
Description: Twelve-year old Chris has a wonderful and thriving childhood with her loving family. When her mother dies tragically in a car accident, she begins to go down a dark spiral. She begins a sinister plan.

Title: Damn! The Duke Got the Wrong Girl
Description: After a passionate night, Ava is stunned to learn Edmund is the new CEO, making her his secretary. She is trapped guarding their secret. Meanwhile, her friend Chloe manipulates Edmund into believing she's his mystery woman.

Title: Pee Nak 4
Description: Three friends find themselves at an old temple located on the outskirts of the city. However, this temple harbours a terrifying legend: anyone who wishes to be ordained as a monk there is cursed.

Title: Kudi Haryane Val Di
Description: A Punjabi man uninterested in wrestling falls for a Haryanvi woman passionate about the sport. He strives to embrace her love for wrestling, to win her heart.

Title: From Russia with Lev
Description: A documentary exploring Lev Parnas' involvement in the Trump-Ukraine scandal that resulted in the former president's impeachment, detailing Parnas' unexpected entanglement with Trump and Giuliani, leading to his incarceration.

Title: Ça arrive
Description: In a police station in Marseille, three investigators work together on fifteen different cases of sexual assaults, while doing their best to remain neutral and professional. Until a familiar face comes in to testify.

Title: Top Floor
Description: 20 million followers = 20 million suspects

Title: Salem Witch Doll
Description: Sarah, a depressed college drop out, must uncover her family's twisted history, and her own greater purpose if she is to defeat the Salem Doll, a monstrous wooden creature that terrorises Sarah and her loved ones.

Title: Bardejov
Description: The story of small town Jewish leader Rafuel Lowy, who found an ingenious way to save Bardejov's Jewish population from being sent to Auschwitz during World War Two.

Title: The Blackwell Ghost 8
Description: A filmmaker continues his quest to uncover the truth behind a series of unsolved murders from years ago. This is the 8th installment of "The Blackwell Ghost" series.

Title: Freaknik: The Wildest Party Never Told
Description: Recounts the rise and fall of a small Atlanta HBCU picnic that exploded into an influential street party and spotlighted ATL as a major cultural stage.

Title: Une vie rêvée
Description: In their council flat in the suburbs of Paris, Nicole (52) and her son, Serge (19), live a fusional love that flourishes against all odds. But as the Christmas holidays approach, turning their relationship and their life upside down.

Title: Finding Tony
Description: When a depressed, widowed NBA star loses everything, he reluctantly begins coaching a junior college women's basketball team, where he meets an orphaned basketball phenom who will change his life forever.

Title: Moartea in vacanta
Description: Death on Holiday follows the story of three characters who become overnight "friends in need" - who desperately try to get into the good graces of a lonely and wealthy old woman, Rodica, hoping to inherit her fortune.

Title: Blacksmith: Alagbede
Description: A blacksmith navigates the rhythms of daily life, finding moments of humor and lightheartedness amidst the steady flow of work and responsibilities.

Title: Mongol
Description: Young Mongol is in love with daughter of his Lord. Her Father condemns him as a criminal and names him an outlaw. Mongol must navigate world full of treachery and deception, fighting for survival and justice.

Title: Mor Chhainha Bhuinya 2
Description: Two brothers Uday and Kartik grow up together in Chhattisgarh with differences in their ideologies but with love for each other in their hearts. One day, they find themselves against each other. What will win, their love or their ideology?

Title: Anatema
Description: Juana descends into the catacombs of Madrid in search of the mythical Seal of San Simeon, accompanied by a priest, a novice and an exorcist. They will face supernatural forces and secrets that threaten to unleash an ancient evil.

Title: Turning
Description: An apathetic former college athlete runs an AirBnB alongside a terminally ill imaginary mother figure when a string of eclectic visitors inspire him to confront his aimlessness.

Title: Ram Bharosey
Description: In a remote village in Gujarat, Keshav and Kesar's secret love story blossoms with handwritten letters and secret meetings, orchestrated by the help of Keshav's friend Parag. During one such meeting, Keshav and Kesar indulge in an intimate encounter. What will happen when Kesar misses her period?

Title: Ship Life
Description: Cruise ships house thousands of crew members from diverse backgrounds, living and working together at sea for extended periods.

Title: My Boyfriend Is a Sex Worker 2
Description: Convinced that his beloved Gio left him for money, Ace's life spirals downward as he drowns his sorrow in a drinking binge. Hopeful a plan devised by Ace's sister, Malou, can reignite their spark while keeping their meddling family at bay.

Title: Abner
Description: It is a story of a teacher's greatest zeal and advocacy to impart his knowledge to the young least fortunates who are deprived of appropriate education. ABNER is a mirror of a man's utmost perseverance against all odds. Thus, the heavens opened its gates for Abner and favored him with so much joy and fulfillment.

Title: 50 km/h
Description: After the death of their father, two brothers separated because of a conflicted relationship between the two, meet at his funeral and it is the perfect opportunity for them to face the demons of the past.

Title: A Kidnapping in Amish Country
Description: An Amish woman's daughter is kidnapped. She seeks help from her estranged friend who left the Amish community and found social media stardom.

Title: Builder Boys
Description: Broker and engineer dream of building but lack funds. Seize redevelopment opportunity in old building, but superstitious real estate tycoon complicates plans.

Title: Alyad Palyad
Description: A group of friends find themselves stranded in an island village during the three days it's believed to be haunted by vengeful spirits, forcing them to confront the dark secrets behind the village's eerie traditions

Title: To Gather Around
Description: Bai Sheng, a veteran Internet firm employee, enters a workplace conflict defending his rights. Joining others to resolve it, he's swept into an even greater mystery.

Title: Agastya - Chapter 1
Description: Saurya is haunted by a difficult past and grapples with his troubled mind. After a year, his brother embarks on a quest to find him. A touching story unfolds as Nisan delves into Saurya's history.

Title: Darling
Description: A tourist office employee, Raghav, inadvertently weds Anandhi while saving for his dream Paris honeymoon, resulting in a series of challenges he must confront.

Title: Bad Director
Description: It follows Gregor Samsa, a washed-up director in his late fifties who is reviewing his life. Him having wasted it as a cultural worker doesn't exactly add to his joy.

Title: Mandara
Description: Mandara, Vishwa's love meets heartbreak. Yashora, orphan heiress, flees murderous uncle seeking fortune. Their paths cross, intertwining love, loss, resilience. Dramatic climax against Sri Lankan backdrop, captivating soundtrack.

Title: Alien Hunt
Description: A group of siblings go to their family cabin after over a decade for a hunting trip to reconnect, only to find themselves being hunted by a terrifying alien creature. Now they must team up and become the hunters before becoming the hunted.

Title: Living with Leopards
Description: A nature documentary that follows two leopard cubs as they make the journey from infancy into adulthood.

Title: Amongst the Wolves
